import React from "react"
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from "react-router-dom"
import Front from "./index"
import Contacto from "./contacto"
import Nosotros from "./nosotros"
import Frutas from "./frutas"
import Verduras from "./verduras"
import "../assets/style/principal.scss"


function App (){
    return(
        <Router>
            <Switch>
                <Route path="/" exact>
                    <Front/>
                </Route>
                <Route path="/contacto">
                    <Contacto/>
                </Route>
                <Route path="/nosotros">
                    <Nosotros/>
                </Route>
                <Route path="/frutas">
                    <Frutas/>
                </Route>
                <Route path="/verduras">
                    <Verduras/>
                </Route>
            </Switch>
        </Router>
    )
}

export default App
